<div id="article-header">

                
		

    
        	    





		
										

        


                		



	    	    	    	    



 	
     	
 	
 	<div id="main-article-info">
 		
					
				
			<h1
																									>Why barefoot is best for children</h1>
				
					<p id="stand-first"
				 class="stand-first-alone"																				>Most parents would balk at the idea of toddlers in high heels, but what about sandals or trainers? Some experts now believe that all shoes are best avoided in childhood, says Sam Murphy<br /><br /><a href="http://www.guardian.co.uk/lifeandstyle/2010/aug/09/is-barefoot-running-good-for-you">Q&amp;A: Is barefoot running good for you?</a></p>
		
				
  	</div>
  	
  	  	            <ul id="content-actions" class="share-links">
                                
    
	
		
													

    
    
        
    <li class="share-links">
        <ul>
    
			
			
	
