    						<li class="b3">
			<a href="http://www.guardian.co.uk/lifeandstyle/2010/aug/09/barefoot-best-for-children#start-of-comments" class="content-comment-count" short-url="-p-2tdp3">Comments (<span class="comment-count-val">&hellip;</span>)</a>
		</li>
