															<li class="first">
																			    


	        <h3>
		
	        Read more
    </h3>
    
																	</li>
														
														
																				
														
															<li class="picture ">
																													    
																																												
			
			
			
			
	
		
						<a href="http://www.guardian.co.uk/lifeandstyle/2010/aug/09/is-barefoot-running-good-for-you"  class="link-image ">
										 
    
    
    	
	<img src="http://static.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Lifeandhealth/Pix/pictures/2010/7/19/1279546267648/Zola-Budd-002.jpg"  width="140" height="84" alt="Zola Budd"
						 />
													</a>
			
		
				
	
										    
																																										
				
		
		
			
						
		<p>
		
	        <a     data-cpt="cpt-239" href="http://www.guardian.co.uk/lifeandstyle/2010/aug/09/is-barefoot-running-good-for-you"  class="link-text">Is barefoot running good for you?</a>
    </p>
					
										    
																																										
				
			
		
			
			<p class="trail-text">
											                        
                                    			Before you throw your running shoes away, read <strong>Evan Fanning</strong>'s barefoot running Q&amp;A
		</p>
	
