				<h1>Why barefoot is best for children</h1>
		   		    									This article was published on
							<a href='http://www.guardian.co.uk/'>guardian.co.uk</a>
							at <time datetime="2010-08-09T00:00BST" pubdate>10.00 BST on Monday 9 August 2010</time>. 
