							<p>@WillPhysio 
</p><p>  Really interesting article. Here's a great blog for anyone interested in Barefoot    
<br clear="none" />  Running: <a shape="rect" href="http://www.hfs-clinics.co.uk/blog/podiatry/barefoot-running/" rel="nofollow">http://www.hfs-clinics.co.uk/blog/podiatry/barefoot-running/</a>
