                        </div>
                    
					<div class="comment-body">
						
							<p>I love going bare foot. I've got small feet so I find it difficult to find comfortable shoes.
</p><p>A benefit of being bare foot is getting air to infections. I got an infected toe whilst living with people who insisted that I wore shoes at all times, even in the house. Despite the fact that there was a nurse who kept giving me stuff to put on my toe, I was in agony for a fortnight and my toe smelt terrible. I had the same complaint a week ago and went barefoot. It was cleared up in two days. 
</p><p>Bingo.</p>
						
					</div>
