							<p>Yes I agree with the thought that the article shouldn't have advertised for the Vivo.. It seems that in this day and age, journalists feel obliged to give some shopping tips for any possible Life and Style subject. Come on people, if you are going to praise walking barefood, stop hidding behing the vivo or the 5 fingers. 
